    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Maya_denoiser_VS.gif\" width=\"1328\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544543186/Maya_denoiser_VS.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431593896&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1328&amp;height=597\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544543186/Maya_denoiser_VS.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431593896&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"2400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544543198\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Maya_denoiser_VS.gif\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/gif\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544543186\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"72e3c029-2309-4475-bdce-45cba188f544\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544543186/Maya_denoiser_VS.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431593896&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=2400&amp;height=1080 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544543186/Maya_denoiser_VS.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431593896&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1328&amp;height=597 1x\"></span><p><br/><br/>Using the Denoiser in Maya requires a number of steps.</p><h3 id=\"DenoiserinMaya-Step1.\"><br/>Step 1.</h3><p>Ensure that in the RenderMan Preferences, Launch denoiser is ticked (it is on by default)</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManForMaya_denoiser_1.jpg\" width=\"829\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544543186/RenderManForMaya_denoiser_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431594128&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=829&amp;height=516\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544543186/RenderManForMaya_denoiser_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431594128&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"671\" data-width=\"1077\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544543213\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForMaya_denoiser_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544543186\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"81737171-7eed-4550-8a2c-2126136e0f23\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544543186/RenderManForMaya_denoiser_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431594128&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1077&amp;height=671 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544543186/RenderManForMaya_denoiser_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431594128&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=829&amp;height=516 1x\"></span><p> </p><p /><h3 id=\"DenoiserinMaya-Step2\">Step 2</h3><p>In RenderMan's AOV tab in the Render Settings, Select Beauty and untick <strong>As RGBA</strong> and enable Denoise. You can then modify the denoiser parameters.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManForMaya_denoiser_2.jpg\" width=\"780\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544543186/RenderManForMaya_denoiser_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431594128&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=780&amp;height=997\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544543186/RenderManForMaya_denoiser_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431594128&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"997\" data-width=\"780\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544543207\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForMaya_denoiser_2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544543186\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a5b2c259-a91d-4875-8485-948f509c6523\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544543186/RenderManForMaya_denoiser_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431594128&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=780&amp;height=997 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544543186/RenderManForMaya_denoiser_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431594128&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=780&amp;height=997 1x\"></span><p> </p><h3 id=\"DenoiserinMaya-Step3\">Step 3</h3><p>Launch a Batch Render from the RenderMan menu and once the frame(s) have been rendered, the denoise process will begin.</p><p />"
